title.en: Oshi (Uso) no Hittou Majutsu-shi-sama ga "Oretachi, Ryou Omoi Dattan da ne" to Dekiai Shitekurun desu ga?!
Cheat Shoujo ga Boukun Seiou ni Dekiai saresou desu ga, Ima wa Mahou ni Muchuu nan desu!!!
Fukigen na Koushaku-sama wa Uso Hakkenki Tsuki Reijou no Torisetsu wo Goshomou desu
Konyakusha ni Sobahi to shite Riyousareru Kurai Nara Majutsushi-sama no Houshou to narimasu
Tsuihousareta Moto Reijou, Mori de Hirotta Ouji ni Dekiaisare Seijo ni Mezameru
Zetsubou Reijou no Karei naru Rikon - Osananajimi no Taikou Kakka no Dekiai ga Tomaranai no desu
Dare ni mo Aisarenai no de Yuka wo Migaite Itara Soko ga Seiiki-ka shita Reijou no Hanashi
Dokushin Shugi no Reijou wa, Koushaku-sama no Dekiai kara Nogaretai
30-sai Toshiue Koushaku no Gosai no Hazu ga Sono Musuko ni Dekiaisareru
Uranaishi ni wa hana kishi no koigokoro ga miete imasu
Wanko-Kei Osananajimi no Kishi ga, Otto ni narimashite
Bikei Ouji ga Nigate na Hatenkou Mobu Reijou wa Jibun Rashiku Ikite Ikitai!
Nise Seijo da to Iwaremashita ga, Douyara Watashi ga Honmono no you desu ka?
Hitomebore to Iwaretanoni Jitsuwa Otorida to Shitta Hakushaku Reijou no Mikkakan
Ikatsui Kao de Kyouaku Kishi Danchou to Osorerareru Koushaku-sama no Saigo no Konkatsu Aite wa Shakoukai no Maboroshi no Hana deshita
Kiraware Tsuma wa, Eiyuu Shougun to Rikon Shitai!
